{"Id":480226,"Title":"尚友斋为旷伯逵赋","Dynasty":"明","Author":"刘崧","Context":"繄予之生，乃后古人。岂不尚友，远而莫因。譬彼方夜，思见出日。狂走大呼，秪益其疾。及求吾心，夫岂远而。昼读其书，夜梦见之。我疑其生，世谓其死。不曰斯今，亦有君子。有鸟有鸟，鸣于高林。彼君子兮，怀之好音。视彼日月，滔滔其迈。人而离居，曷云不戒。闻子今日，涉江远来。何以来思，赠之琼瑰。穆穆其风，菀菀者柳。何以永日，且以酌酒。汎汎中流，招之以舟。一日不见，余心则忧。居则同襺，出则更屧。云胡拒之，彼则有挟。我友旷逵，友道则隆。维彼所尚，实获我同。蓬依于麻，禾乱于莠。嗟尔君子，式尚尔友。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"9a157c460e207fb90f70572a6d47b187","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6506302,"Sentence":"繄予之生，乃后古人。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yī yú zhī shēng ，nǎi hòu gǔ rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506303,"Sentence":"岂不尚友，远而莫因。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qi bú shàng yǒu ，yuǎn ér mò yīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506304,"Sentence":"譬彼方夜，思见出日。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"pì bi fāng yè ，sāi jiàn chū rì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506305,"Sentence":"狂走大呼，秪益其疾。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"kuáng zǒu dà hū ，zhī yì jī jǐ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506306,"Sentence":"及求吾心，夫岂远而。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jǐ qǐu wú xīn ，fū qi yuǎn ér ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506307,"Sentence":"昼读其书，夜梦见之。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhòu dòu jī shū ，yè mèng jiàn zhī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506308,"Sentence":"我疑其生，世谓其死。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ yǐ jī shēng ，shì wèi jī si ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506309,"Sentence":"不曰斯今，亦有君子。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bú yuē sī jīn ，yì yǒu jūn zi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6506310,"Sentence":"有鸟有鸟，鸣于高林。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu diǎo yǒu diǎo ，mǐng yú gāo lǐn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":